00:33:02,332 --> 00:33:05,115
[SPEAKER_05]: She is the entity who shares my other consciousness.

405
00:33:05,695 --> 00:33:09,739
[SPEAKER_05]: When she is out of sorts, when I am sanguine, we confuse each other.

406
00:33:10,159 --> 00:33:11,921
[SPEAKER_05]: But sometimes it's the other way around.

407
00:33:12,461 --> 00:33:14,142
